text: Newly-opened MRT station serving the namesake Tanjong Rhu area. The station is also within walking distance of the Singapore Indoor Stadium and the National Stadium.
Scenes around the Tanjong Rhu MRT Station, on the Thomson East Coast Line, newly opened end of June.
